        </div>
        
        <div class="footer-bottom">
            <p>United Bus Pro is a premier private transportation and shuttle logistics provider. All operations prioritize safety, reliability, and passenger comfort.</p>
            <div style="display: flex; gap: 15px; font-size: 1.5rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);">
                <i class="fab fa-cc-visa"></i>
                <i class="fab fa-cc-mastercard"></i>
                <i class="fab fa-cc-amex"></i>
